      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAXIMUM DAMAGE (3) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage 1.5 lengths away in third (30.28). Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. One of the contenders. PRETTY ESMAY (4) finds it hard to break through. Has hit the frame the last two runs, the latest when second (31.84) at this track. Overdue and is among the main hopes. WHO KNOWS REG (6) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 375m behind Skedaddle Benny (22.94) in a Grade 3/4. Was in the money the start prior. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from eight starts. Should be about the money. WHODAT HOOKED (1) can feature with the right run.",
